467
00:37:10,350 --> 00:37:14,920
to be faithful people that live in the world

468
00:37:14,920 --> 00:37:20,410
but not of it for His sake, for Jesus.

469
00:37:21,510 --> 00:37:23,610
He loved us so much that He would die for us,

470
00:37:23,710 --> 00:37:27,640
take our sin, take all of our selfishness,

471
00:37:27,640 --> 00:37:30,520
take our affluenza, take it all to the cross

472
00:37:30,520 --> 00:37:33,580
and leave it there and nail it there.

473
00:37:34,730 --> 00:37:38,180
We might be free, free to live, free to give,

474
00:37:38,380 --> 00:37:40,660
free to experience God in the now.

475
00:37:42,270 --> 00:37:44,370
Knowing our past is secure, our future is secure.

476
00:37:44,670 --> 00:37:47,400
and we'll be with Him forever.

477
00:37:49,330 --> 00:37:50,390
Oh, what a God we serve.

478
00:37:51,710 --> 00:37:53,770
Oh, what a great God of love that would give it all

479
00:37:53,770 --> 00:37:57,450
and stretched out His arms this wide and gave it all for us.

480
00:37:58,360 --> 00:37:58,980
Let us pray.

481
00:38:00,440 --> 00:38:01,360
Our Heavenly Father,

482
00:38:05,000 --> 00:38:08,670
Your very character is a God who gives.

483
00:38:11,400 --> 00:38:12,860
You gave Your one and only Son

484
00:38:12,860 --> 00:38:17,040
that whoever believes in You would have eternal life

485
00:38:17,040 --> 00:38:19,800
and we'd never perish.

486
00:38:21,630 --> 00:38:22,990
Thank You for You.

487
00:38:23,830 --> 00:38:24,990
Thank You for Jesus

488
00:38:24,990 --> 00:38:30,050
and the sacrifice that You made for us.

489
00:38:32,980 --> 00:38:34,420
And so, Lord, as we take these elements,

490
00:38:34,980 --> 00:38:36,660
may You impress upon us again

491
00:38:36,660 --> 00:38:37,900
the depth of Your love

492
00:38:37,900 --> 00:38:39,760
and the depth of Your sacrifice,

493
00:38:40,320 --> 00:38:43,920
the depth of Your giving to us and for us.

494
00:38:45,480 --> 00:38:48,020
And may that cause us to love You more,

495
00:38:48,260 --> 00:38:49,420
to worship You more,

496
00:38:49,820 --> 00:38:52,320
to seek You out more and more.

497
00:38:54,700 --> 00:38:55,900
So meet us here, we pray.

498
00:38:57,140 --> 00:38:58,460
In Jesus' name we pray.

499
00:38:59,520 --> 00:38:59,820
Amen.

